data.description: LOWERED PRICE...Move-in Ready 2018, Only one owner has lived in this  two-story 4 bedroom-2.5 bath! This home also features a conservation/pond back yard. Enjoy Florida wildlife at its best. No rear neighbors. In addition there is an office/flex space that can be used by those fortunate enough to work from home, or toy room, guest bedroom, you decide. Large screened in lanai to have that first cup of coffee or evening beverage watching the sunset. It is equipped with solar system that keeps your electric bills at an all-time low.  The amazing layout offers 2,614 square feet of living space, and 3398 total under roof including oversized covered porch. driveway is oversized and can fit 4 cars plus your 2 car garage, this house is ready for entertaining.  This popular open concept with Living, Dining, and Family Rooms as well as Kitchen that boasts a Kitchen Island, Walk-In Pantry, and stunning Cabinetry with plenty of room for everything still has the new-home feel! It also boasts stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting. Breakfast Nook adds even more room, making this perfect for entertaining or family gatherings too! Spacious Owners Suite allows room for furniture of all sizes, with Master Bath that include two separate sinks with extra drawer space below, linen closet and large Walk-In Closet. Roomy secondary bedrooms allow plenty of flexibility as well! The back access features sliding doors into the lanai with a large area to entertain with fire pit or for future pool in this premium lot! Wonderful office with lots of natural light is on the first floor for those fortunate enough to work remotely.  All bedrooms and good-sized laundry room are on the 2nd level. Secondary living space is upstairs too.  It is nestled in the exclusive community of Cypress Creek an open-air clubhouse, pools cabana, basketball courts, dog parks, fitness center and playgrounds. RESORT STYLE AMENITIES which includes ULTRIFI CABLE AND HIGH-SPEED INTERNET with your low, quarterly HOA fee. The natural lighting is amazing reminding you of the Florida lifestyle. This home is conveniently located near I-75, U.S HWY 301 and 41, near hospitals, major shopping centers, minutes away from the beach, dinning, entertainment and more! Don't wait, call for a private tour today. NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED This is a must see home!
